        {
            "title": "花旗利率交易團隊認為市場低估了美國通膨回升的風險",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"592\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/nRO5EPfjf4jxXp72x.yZ8Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU5Mg--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/17a271464fd25948cde2fe35cdd83e77\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 花旗集團利率團隊認為，市場對美國<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:通膨;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/通膨\">通膨</a>前景過於自滿，在物價壓力回升時獲利的交易因此具有吸引力。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">花旗利率交易部門策略師Benjamin <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:Wiltshire;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/Wiltshire\">Wiltshire</a>表示，投資者可能低估了美國消費者的韌性，市場對通膨的預期很可能會小幅上修。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「市場似乎堅信通膨會降下來，」Wiltshire在接受採訪時表示。「但我們仍處在一個通膨率結構性更高的環境裡。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Wiltshire建議買入5y5y通膨遠期，他認為當前約2.5%的水平偏低。眼下通膨仍高於這一水平 —— 聯儲會偏好的「基本通膨」衡量指標依然頑固，仍位於不到3%的水平。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-d797aeaa-233b-3c79-b185-d5d9cdc23044-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"592\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/zSe3cb2dq4r0kXAm0rzV0Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU5Mg--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/8a7ba24456c2e36e9ef0af2c8e077c26\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：美國主導的通膨回潮恐是市場最大盲點 貝萊德、橋水等巨頭已搶先佈局</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">上述觀點發布之際，周三強於預期的美國就業數據令投資者感到意外，美債殖利率攀升，交易員隨之下調了對聯儲會年內降息的預期。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">周四美國國債趨於穩定，10年期殖利率下跌1個基點至4.17%。交易員接下來將關注當日稍晚公佈的初請失業金人數數據，以進一步衡量經濟狀況；而1月消費者價格通膨數據將於周五公佈。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Wiltshire稱，鑒於去年美國關稅政策未出現許多人預期的快速傳導效應，市場不願意計入更高的通膨風險。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">他說：「去給通膨溢價定價的勁頭並不存在。我認為從結構上看，通膨風險被低估了。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Citigroup Rates Desk Says Market Is Too Calm About US Inflation</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%8A%B1%E6%97%97%E5%88%A9%E7%8E%87%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E5%9C%98%E9%9A%8A%E8%AA%8D%E7%82%BA%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4%E4%BD%8E%E4%BC%B0%E4%BA%86%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%80%9A%E8%86%A8%E5%9B%9E%E5%8D%87%E7%9A%84%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA-131529487.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-02-12 22:07:42",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
